We’re running into an issue with our auto where after finishing a path the auto doesn’t continue to the next one. After running running our “Score J to human” the robot stops and doesn’t continue to the “Human to L.5” path. However when we run a sperate auto with just the “Human to L.5” that path runs. We tried adding a namedCommand after “Score J to human” and it ran but “Human to L.5” still didn’t run.
